#. Tag: title
#: compare.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Compare</title>"
msgstr "<title>तूल</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: compare.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krusader; contains several compare functions: <guimenuitem>Compare by "
"Content</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Compare Folders</guimenuitem> and the "
"<link linkend=\"synchronizer\">Synchronizer</link> compare function."
msgstr ""
"&amp;krusader; अनेकाः तुलनाकार्यं समाविष्टाः सन्ति:<guimenuitem> सामग्रीद्वारा तुलनां "
"कुरुत</guimenuitem> , ९.<guimenuitem> Folders इत्यस्य तुलनां कुर्वन्तु</guimenuitem> "
"तथा<link linkend=\"synchronizer\"> समन्वयक</link> compare function."

#. Tag: title
#: compare.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compare by Content"
msgstr "सामग्रीद्वारा तुलनां कुरुत"

#. Tag: primary
#: compare.docbook:17 compare.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Compare</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>तुलना</primary> इति"

#. Tag: secondary
#: compare.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid "Content"
msgstr "विषयः"

#. Tag: para
#: compare.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select one file in each panel and use <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Compare by content...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. &krusader; "
"will open an external graphical difference tool that is <link linkend="
"\"konfig-dependencies\">configured</link>. &kompare;, <ulink url=\"https://"
"www.kde.org/applications/development/kdiff3/\"><application>KDiff3</"
"application></ulink> and <ulink url=\"http://furius.ca/xxdiff/"
"\"><application>xxdiff</application></ulink> are supported."
msgstr ""
"प्रत्येकस्मिन् पटले एकां सञ्चिकां चित्वा उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु<menuchoice><guimenu> संचिका</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem> सामग्रीद्वारा तुलनां कुर्वन्तु...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> . "
"&amp;krusader; बाह्यं चित्रात्मकं भेदसाधनं उद्घाटयिष्यति यत् अस्ति<link linkend="
"\"konfig-dependencies\"> विन्यस्तम्</link> . &amp;कम्परे;, २.<ulink url=\"https://"
"www.kde.org/applications/development/kdiff3/\"><application> KDiff3</"
"application></ulink> तथा<ulink url=\"http://furius.ca/xxdiff/"
"\"><application> xxdiff</application></ulink> समर्थिताः भवन्ति।"

#. Tag: title
#: compare.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compare Folders"
msgstr "Folders इत्यस्य तुलनां कुर्वन्तु"

#. Tag: secondary
#: compare.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folders"
msgstr "पुटम्"

#. Tag: para
#: compare.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Compare the files of each panel by using <menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Compare Folders</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. By "
"default newer and single files will be selected in each panel, this "
"behaviour can be changed in the <guimenuitem>Compare Setup</guimenuitem> "
"menu."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>पुटस्य तुलनां कुर्वन्तु</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> इत्यस्य उपयोगेन प्रत्येकस्य पटलस्य सञ्चिकानां तुलनां कुर्वन्तु । "
"पूर्वनिर्धारितरूपेण प्रत्येकस्मिन् पटले नूतनाः एकसञ्चिकाः च चयनिताः भविष्यन्ति, एषः व्यवहारः "
"<guimenuitem>Compare Setup</guimenuitem> मेन्यू मध्ये परिवर्तयितुं शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: compare.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The files are not compared by content but by their names and dates only."
msgstr "सञ्चिकानां तुलना सामग्रीद्वारा न अपितु केवलं तेषां नामभिः तिथिभिः च क्रियते ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: compare.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Compare Setup</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सम्पादनं</guimenu> <guimenuitem>सेटअपस्य तुलनां कुरुत</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: compare.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configures the <guimenuitem>Compare Folders</guimenuitem> function."
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Compare Folders</guimenuitem> कार्यं विन्यस्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: compare.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Select Newer and Single</guimenuitem> (default)"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>नवीनतरं एककं च चिनोतु</guimenuitem> (पूर्वनिर्धारितम्)"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: compare.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select Single"
msgstr "Single इति चिनोतु"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: compare.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select Newer"
msgstr "नवीनतरं चिनोतु"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: compare.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select Different and Single"
msgstr "भिन्नं एककं च चिनोतु"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: compare.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select Different"
msgstr "भिन्नं चिनोतु"
